<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8205378>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Plesioxylion gambianus (Borowski, 2018) gen. et comb. nov., ♂ (RBINS beside C in LYL). A. Dorsal view. B. Front view of head and pronotum. C. Lateral view. D. Posterior view of elytral declivity. E. Ventral view. Scale bar: A, C, E = 1 mm; B, D = 0.75 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8205378/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8205380>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Plesioxylion gambianus (Borowski, 2018) gen. et comb. nov., ♂. Last visible abdominal segment and aedeagus. A. Ventral view of last tergite.B. Posterior view of aedeagus. C. Ventral view of aedeagus. D. Dorsal view of aedeagus. E. Rear view of last ventrite. Abbreviations: b = basal piece; p = paramere (refer to Lesne 1940)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8205380/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8205382>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Plesioxylion gambianus (Borowski, 2018) gen. et comb. nov., ♀ (LYL). A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C. Lateral view. D. Ventral view of abdominal ventrites. E. Postero-lateral view of elytral declivity. Scale bar: A–C = 1 mm; D–E = 0.75 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8205382/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8205384>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Declivity of female of the representatives of selected genera. A. Plesioxylion gambianus (Borowski, 2018) gen. et comb. nov.B. Mesoxylion collaris(Erichson, 1842). C. Amintinus minutissimus Damoiseau, 1968. D. Xylion securifer Lesne, 1901." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8205384/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

